    <S id="S_0">
        <FORM>nuten mikon mikon ia er aranai cu ku na Nʉ'ʉvana mosa na Tanganua kanakana'ua maku Miciku rovʉvʉ.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh"> 若要米貢的時候，我就從瑪雅里去達卡努瓦里去拜訪我姊姊Miciku。</TRANSL>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="en"> During the rice ceremony, I went from NU'Uvana to Tanganua to visit my older sister Miciku.</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="kkvNr_mikon_Kuatu_S0.mp3" url="https://formosanbank.linguistics.ntu.edu.tw/files/audio/kkvNr_mikon_Kuatu.mp3"/>
