    <S id="S_4">
        <FORM>er kumakʉnʉ kia er makasua cu er matacuvucuvun cu ha cau er tia kaisisi.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh"> 我們就那樣吃著，人們聚在一塊要祭祀。</TRANSL>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="en"> We kept eating in that way, and people gathered together to worship.</TRANSL>
